author: Pamela Muse
text:
An Alliance member is interested in learning about cities/counties that have created inter-jurisdictional/multi-jurisdictional GIS services relationships.
If you have implemented/provide/participate in an inter-jurisdictional/multi-jurisdictional  GIS services arrangements please share agreements, policies, etc and the contact information to follow-up with.
Thank you,
Pam
